    dc:creator "Davies, Kerrie A.; Giblin-Davis, Robin M.; Ye, Weimin; Taylor, Gary S.; Thomas, W. Kelley" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Nematodes from galls on Myrtaceae. V. Fergusobia from large multilocular shoot bud galls from Angophora and Eucalyptus in Australia, with descriptions of six new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221902>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221903>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221898> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221902>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Fergusobia pimpamensis n. sp. ex A. nr. woodsiana (all in lateral view): A, Entire parthenogenetic female; B, Head of parthenogenetic female; C, Habitus; D, Tails of parthenogenetic females; E, Entire infective female; F, Head of infective female; G; Habitus; H, Tails of infective females; I, Entire male; J, Head of male; K, Habitus; L, Tails of males. Scale bars: A, E, I = 50 µm. B, F, J = 5 µm. Tails not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221903>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Habitus drawings of Fergusobia spp. collected from large multilocular leaf bud galls: A— F. floribundae n. sp. from Angophora floribunda; B— F. pimpamensis n. sp. from Angophora sp; C—undescribed species from E. nr. acmenioides; D—undescribed species from E. amygdalina; E— F. delegatensisae n. sp. from E. delegatensis; F—undescribed species from E. pauciflora; G—undescribed species from E. racemosa; H—undescribed species from E. obliqua; I— F. diversifoliae n. sp. from E. diversifolia; J—undescribed species from E. blakelyi; K— F. brittenae from E. camaldulensis; L—undescribed species from E. dealbata; M— F. minimus n. sp. from E. tereticornis; N— F. cosmophyllae n. sp. from E. cosmophylla; O—undescribed species from E. robusta; P—undescribed species from Eucalyptus sp. at Woodburn, NSW. Scale bars = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.221898>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Scanning electron micrographs of Fergusobia spp. from large multilocular shoot bud galls. A, B F. pimpamensis n. sp.; C, D F. delegatensae n. sp. A, Head (en face); B, vulva and lateral field; C Head (en face); D, Head (lateral view). Scale bars: A, C = 2 µm; B = 10 µm; C = 5 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/221898/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

